 ############################
 MOUNTING
 ############################

 To mount flash it is necessary to type next command
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 |#mount -t vfat /dev/sdc1 /media/flash -o iocharset=koi8-r,codepage=866 |
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 or
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 |# mount -t vfat /dev/sdc1 /mnt/flash 					|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------

